緣起 資料來源

rawData = read.csv('1.CSV', header = TRUE)

for(yid in c(1:length(rawData[,1])))
{
  barplot(as.matrix(rawData[yid,c(-1,-2)]),
          main = paste0("國立台灣大學",
                        rawData[yid,1],
                        "年總計",
                        rawData[yid,2],
                        "人")
  )
}
